These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: sudoku, rock-climbing
Job: project-manager, chef
1. Job:project-manager is in an even position##4
2. Job:chef == Hobby:rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | sudoku |
| Job     | chef    | project-manager   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: 7up, sprite
Sport: lacrosse, cricket
1. Sport:lacrosse is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:sprite is on the left of Beverage:7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | sprite | 7up        |
| Sport      | lacrosse  | cricket |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
